# LinAlgLite

Modern C++17 header-only linear algebra library with optional BLAS backend.

## Features

- Templated `Matrix<T, Rows, Cols>` with static/dynamic sizes
- Row-major storage (only)
- Expression templates for basic arithmetic
- Core operations: transpose, dot, cross, norm, determinant, inverse
- LU decomposition and solve API
- GoogleTest unit tests

## Build

```
cmake -S . -B build -DMYLIB_BUILD_TESTS=ON -DMYLIB_BUILD_EXAMPLES=ON
cmake --build build -j
ctest --test-dir build
```

## Install

```
cmake --install build --prefix /your/prefix
```

Then in another project:

```
find_package(MyLinAlg REQUIRED)
target_link_libraries(your_target PRIVATE MyLinAlg::MyLinAlg)
```
